Query: SELECT b.bid, b.bbalance,        COUNT(DISTINCT a.aid) AS num_accounts,        SUM(a.abalance) AS total_account_balance,        COUNT(DISTINCT t.tid) AS num_tellers,        COUNT(h.tid) AS num_transactions FROM pgbench_branches b LEFT JOIN pgbench_accounts a ON a.bid = b.bid LEFT JOIN pgbench_tellers t ON t.bid = b.bid LEFT JOIN pgbench_history h ON h.bid = b.bid GROUP BY b.bid, b.bbalance ORDER BY b.bid

+-----+----------+--------------+-----------------------+-------------+------------------+
| bid | bbalance | num_accounts | total_account_balance | num_tellers | num_transactions |
